<div class="app-card-container">
	<div class="card">
		<h1>About Me</h1>
		<hr>
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-md-4">
				<%= image_tag 'profile.jpg', class: 'profile-image', alt: 'Profile Image' %>

				<div class="skills">
					<% @skills.each do |skill| %>
						<div class="skill">
							<h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
							<div class="progress">
								<div 
								class="progress-bar bg-success" 
								role="progressbar" 
								aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
								aria-valuemax="100"
								style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%">
								<%= skill.percent_utilized %>%
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					<% end %>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="col-md-8">
				<p>I started coding HTML by hand while in college. I went on to do tech support for Macromedia software, mainly Flash and Dreamweaver, which are now part of Adobe's software suite. While employed with Macromedia I took some courses in Java and C++ as well as attempted to teach myself PHP and MySQL through books.</p>
				<p>Later I went on to take classes in HTML5, CSS3, PHP, MySQL, WordPress, JavaScript, and jQuery through Brookhaven College. I've also done Team Treehouse, where I started with Ruby on Rails. In this industry you never stop learning. I know I don't. I continue to learn through videos and books.</p>

				<p>
					<button class="btn btn-primary" type="button"
					data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#jobHistory"
					aria-expanded="false" aria-controler="jobHistory">
						Job History
					</button>
				
					<button class="btn btn-primary" type="button"
					data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#education"
					aria-expanded="false" aria-controler="education">
						Education
					</button>
				</p>

				<p>
					<div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
						<div class="card card-block">
							Job 1
						</div>
						<div class="card card-block">
							Job 2
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="collapse" id="education">
						<div class="card card-block">
							School 1
						</div>
						<div class="card card-block">
							School 2
						</div>
						<div class="card card-block">
							School 3
						</div>
					</div>
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>



